
Some properties of bitwise operations :

    a |b = a^b + a&b
    a^(a&b) = (a|b)^b
    b^(a&b) = (a|b)^a
    (a&b)^(a|b) = a^b

Addition :

    a+b = a|b + a&b
    a+b = a^b + 2(a&b)

Subtraction :

    a-b = (a^(a&b))-((a|b)^a)
    a-b = ((a|b)^b)-((a|b)^a)
    a-b = (a^(a&b))-(b^(a&b))
    a-b = ((a|b)^b)-(b^(a&b))
